{"tid":1782335,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美中達成貿易協議 參院民主黨領袖稱特朗普向中國屈服","createTime":"2019-12-14T01:17:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-14T03:11:08.000Z","uid":254383,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1af1635280078f4d650aa95579a7912cd31f3aa8","tid":1782335,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T01:17:09.000Z","msg":"民主黨嫌唔夠辣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美国国会参议院民主党领袖星期五(12月13日)声称，特朗普与中国达成贸易协议是向中国屈服。但是一些共和党领袖欢呼特朗普总统取得的成就。<br />\n<br />\n参议院少数党领袖、来自纽约州的查克&middot;舒默 (Chuck Schumer, D-NY）和其他一些民主党人一直在贸易问题上支持特朗普对中国的强硬做法。在传出美中达成第一阶段贸易协议的消息后，舒默发推说：&ldquo;<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">特朗普总统因为中国提出的购买一些大豆的临时而不可靠的承诺而被收买了</span></strong>。这再次表明，无法依赖特朗普总统来为美国的工人和公司做正确的事情。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n议院外交委员会成员、来自康涅狄克州的民主党人克里斯&middot;默菲(Sen. Chris Murphy, D-CT)星期五发表声明，抨击特朗普的协议是向中国&ldquo;投降&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n默菲的声明说：&ldquo;特朗普刚刚宣布的协议恰恰是我们担心的结果。特朗普独自一人用关税灭掉了30万个就业岗位，把美国经济拖下水，而这项协议没有让中国做出任何结构性改革的承诺。特朗普让我们经历这场经济地狱，到底为了什么？&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n他的声明还说：&ldquo;这是经典的唐纳德&middot;特朗普---为了作秀把危机升级，又出于政治权宜，在美国一无所获的情况下，把危机降下来。他总是这样做，而付出代价的是美国家庭。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voachinese.com/amp/senator-schumer-blasts-trump-china-deal-as-sold-out-20191213/5205315.html?__twitter_impression=true\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voachinese.com%2Famp%2Fsenator-schumer-blasts-trump-china-deal-as-sold-out-20191213%2F5205315.html%3F__twitter_impression%3Dtrue&d=wPrcUaBjKD1L%2BB1JqNzGIODrFCZ%2FFQqiuLijmhCLlc8%3D&h=3b59b924\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.voachinese.com/amp/senator-schumer-blasts-trump-china-deal-as-sold-out-20191213/5205315.html?__twitter_impression=true</a>"},{"pid":"9f6fd85abefe4e9eff208aa662ca7f6f4280c3fe","tid":1782335,"uid":13503,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T01:18:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j925w2n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj925w2n.png&h=8639854a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大陸人咁開心就知道唔夠辣"},{"pid":"8bc9167c399245f9a65e3d1a60077da574c5cf0e","tid":1782335,"uid":251769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T01:19:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nJJMgut.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnJJMgut.jpg&h=f3b7947c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c7a976cf6385716c5b8be0149c483fff822e8980","tid":1782335,"uid":97518,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T03:06:33.000Z","msg":"乜唔係澄清左係fake news 咩，好混亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eea5ed7c9b6bc97bca342d383c1fe1eba0c756d8","tid":1782335,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7a976cf6385716c5b8be0149c483fff822e8980","tid":1782335,"uid":97518,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T03:06:33.000Z","msg":"乜唔係澄清左係fake news 咩，好混亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T03:11:08.000Z","msg":"民主黨嫌現有deal唔夠辣"}]}